 23 时许 120 抵达现场 SU7 高速上碰撞爆燃致 3 死，小米公布事件细节"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-9bed46cf378125b86833dd2c057b9291_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "109 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1890446748742285164"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIqeruk6Ws7cZGEAMaCTExNDI4MDQ5OSCb066/BjAAOOMDQAxyEzE4OTA0NDY3NDg3NDIyODUxNjR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1743581752.72296", "card_id": "Q_1890530245590872712", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 2081}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "雷军回应「SU7 车祸致 3 死」事故，称小米不会回避，将持续配合警方调查，哪些信息值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "雷军回应「SU7 爆燃致 3 死」事故"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-9c0ca27c0ac48983eed1001135b0b095_1440w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "109 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1890530245590872712"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIqeruk6Ws7cZGEAMaCTExNDI4NTQ1OSDe7q+/BjAAOI4ZQA1yEzE4OTA1MzAyNDU1OTA4NzI3MTJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1743581752.75108", "card_id": "Q_1890316312032551107", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 18}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价《原神》5.5 版本大活动《荣花竞捷之争》？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-6767a971371dc49682205cc7ec506644_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "107 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B730